        {
            "id": 6048637,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 成信實業*-創(6969)急拉4.01%報40.95元，成交47張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>成信實業*-創(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6969:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6969\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6969-TW</a>)近5分K漲速4.01%，03日10:34報40.95元，成交47張，今日漲幅為3.54％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>成信實業*-創(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6969:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6969\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6969-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲14.14%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+9 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：0 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+9 張</li> </ul></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
