            "title": "《A股焦點》國家全鏈條支持創新藥發展,概念板漲幅領先",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社3日專訊》7月1日,國家醫保局、國家衛生健康委聯合印發《支持創新藥高質量發展的若干措施》,聚焦創新藥發展面臨的突出問題,提出5方面16條措施,對創新藥研發、准入、入院使用和多元支付進行全鏈條支持。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　利好政策密集出台,市場分析機構指創新藥行業基本面持續向好,甚至確定性還在不斷增加。早盤創新藥板塊升幅靠前,九芝堂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000989-CN</a>)、未名醫藥(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002581:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002581\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002581-CN</a>)漲停,神州細胞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:688520:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/688520\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">688520-CN</a>)飆17.8%,賽升藥業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300485:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300485\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300485-CN</a>)升14.6%,長春高新(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000661-CN</a>)升9%,微芯生物(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:688321:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/688321\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">688321-CN</a>)、以岭藥業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002603:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002603\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002603-CN</a>)、舒泰神(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300204:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300204\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300204-CN</a>)跟漲。(ry)</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
